---
import PageShell from '../components/PageShell.astro';
---

<PageShell
  title="Accessibility · Forty Years of Transformation"
  description="The accessibility statement, conformance target, and language options for the Forty Years of Transformation record."
  path="/accessibility"
>
  <section class="page-section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <p class="eyebrow">Accessibility</p>
      <h1>Built to be read by everyone.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        This record targets WCAG 2.2 Level AA. It is designed to be readable
        without JavaScript, navigable by keyboard alone, and safe for people who
        prefer reduced motion.
      </p>

      <h2>What we've built in</h2>
      <ul class="a11y-list">
        <li>Text contrast of at least 4.5:1 for body copy and 3:1 for large text and UI, including the mist-bright body colour used on the dark chapters.</li>
        <li>A visible 2px gold focus outline with a 2px offset on every interactive element — links, buttons, region nodes, filmstrip controls.</li>
        <li>A skip-to-content link as the first focusable element on every page.</li>
        <li>Semantic landmarks (header, nav, main, footer) and a single, correctly-ordered heading per page.</li>
        <li>Full keyboard operability for the chapter navigation, the regional map, and the archive filmstrip — none of them trap focus.</li>
        <li>A complete <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> fallback: the transformation spine is drawn statically, ledger figures show their final value immediately, and parallax, pinning and Ken-Burns effects are all disabled.</li>
        <li>Descriptive alt text on every content image; decorative graphics are marked <code>aria-hidden</code>.</li>
        <li>A readable, unstyled fallback for visitors without JavaScript — all copy and figures are present in the page's initial HTML.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="language">Language</h2>
      <p>
        The record is published in English. Copy is held in typed content
        collections so it can be translated without touching layout code;
        Luganda and Kiswahili are reserved as the next languages to ship.
      </p>
      <div class="footer-lang" role="group" aria-label="Language">
        <button type="button" aria-current="true">English</button>
        <button type="button" disabled title="Coming soon">Luganda</button>
        <button type="button" disabled title="Coming soon">Kiswahili</button>
      </div>

      <h2 id="privacy">Privacy &amp; cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This record sets no third-party cookies and runs no third-party
        trackers. If you accept the analytics prompt, a self-hosted,
        cookie-free visit counter records which chapters are read — no IP
        address, no personal data, no cross-site tracking. Declining changes
        nothing about how the record works; every chapter, figure and download
        remains fully available either way.
      </p>

      <h2>Reporting an issue</h2>
      <p>
        If you encounter an accessibility barrier anywhere on this record, please
        contact the Office of the President so it can be corrected. Include the
        page, the assistive technology or browser you were using, and what you
        expected to happen.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageShell>

<style>
  .page-section {
    padding-block: var(--space-32) var(--space-24);
    background: var(--veil-navy);
    min-height: 60vh;
  }
  .wrap {
    max-width: var(--content-max);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: var(--page-margin);
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    max-width: 20ch;
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 var(--space-6);
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-body-l);
    max-width: 60ch;
    color: var(--mist-bright);
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    margin-top: var(--space-16);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    border-top: var(--border-gold-hairline);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
  }
  .a11y-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    max-width: 68ch;
    padding-left: 1.2em;
  }
  code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85em;
    color: var(--gold-hi);
  }
  .footer-lang {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }
  .footer-lang button {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    background: none;
    border: var(--border-hairline);
    color: var(--mist);
    padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-control);
  }
  .footer-lang button[aria-current='true'] {
    color: var(--gold-hi);
    border-color: var(--gold-hairline);
  }
  .footer-lang button:disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
  }
</style>
